			<link>https://culturall1.idrc.ocadu.ca/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=90&amp;catid=15&amp;Itemid=53</link>
			<description><![CDATA[<ol><li><div align="left">Fully keyboard navigable (including visual indicators of focus, etc.)</div></li><li><div align="left">Enhanced keyboard navigation allows the author to move easily between the button bars, content being edited, and the status bar.</div></li><li><div align="left">All buttons in user interface have alt-text.</div></li><li><div align="left">Prompting for accessibility labels for images, table information.&nbsp;</div></li><li><div align="left"><a href="https://culturall1.idrc.ocadu.ca/index.php?option=com_content&amp;task=view&amp;id=71&amp;Itemid=35">Plug-in for Checking Accessibility (AChecker)</a></div></li><li><div align="left">Enhanced references to accessibility in the documentation.</div></li></ol><p align="left">{mosimage}</p>]]></description>
